<section class="known-site-section" id="architecture">
    <div class="known-site-section-head">
        <span>项目结构</span>
        <h2>围绕核心库与多端宿主构建生态</h2>
        <p>框架核心、插件项目与不同宿主工程职责清晰，便于拆分、复用与发布。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="known-site-grid known-site-grid-2">
        <article class="known-site-card known-site-card-accent">
            <h3>核心与插件</h3>
            <ul class="known-site-list">
                <li><strong>Known</strong>：核心类库，提供对象模型、组件、扩展、权限、工作流。</li>
                <li><strong>Plugins/</strong>：插件目录，支持核心服务、Excel 能力与示例模块扩展。</li>
                <li><strong>AutoPage</strong>：自动页面与配置化能力，提升交付效率。</li>
            </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="known-site-card known-site-card-accent">
            <h3>多端宿主</h3>
            <ul class="known-site-list">
                <li><strong>Known.Server</strong>：Server 模式示例与部署入口。</li>
                <li><strong>Known.Wasm / Known.WasmHost</strong>：WebAssembly 前后端宿主。</li>
                <li><strong>Known.WinForm / Known.Maui / Known.Photino</strong>：桌面与移动端承载。</li>
            </ul>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>
